title: #92Noon Live from TCO! Wobby/Mehta/Birk/Zimmer Presser
description: It's another Wednesday show LIVE from TCO Performance Center in Eagan! Wobby starts off the show, Manish Mehta from the New York Daily News previews the Jets-Vikings game on Sunday, Mike Zimmer conducts his weekly presser, and Matt Birk stops by the TCO Studios as well!
